relation: Flint's dog, from EB64. I always thought he was nifty. I really like how this one turned out.

Inspired by Gonmon's Boogie Tent I was thinking that the original game tent could have looked more interesting had it had a yellow-purple striped pattern. Plus, i was always a little miffed that all you saw were the mouth and eyes of the Boogie Tent, so I drew this up.
Pokey Bot. Just a little OpenCanvas sketch, really.
Bow-wow Fish. I really enjoy how the colouring turned out on this one.
